title: Medicine Singers - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Medicine Singers performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded July 11, 2023.

Songs:
Calumet
Rumble
Midnight
Honor Song

This performance is dedicated to Ms. Kat, Kathleen "Spirit Dancer" Patricia DeGraw Mann Crippen, Ramapough Lenape, Wolf Clan

Daryl Black Eagle Jamieson - Vocals, Powwow Drum
Daniel Monkman aka Zoon - Vocals, Powwow Drum
Artie Red Medicine Crippen - Vocals, Powwow Drum
Dean Running Deer Robinson - Vocals, Powwow Drum
Yonatan Gat - Guitar, Rhodes
Christopher Pravdica - Bass
Gal Lazer - Drums
Cinque "ignabu" Kemp - Drums

Host: Larry Mizell, Jr.
Audio Engineers: Kevin Suggs
Audio Mixer: Yonatan Gat
Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro, Ettie Wahl
Editor: Jim Beckmann
